<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-259] Ability to parse EJB QL multiline queries in orm.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-259</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Multiline queries in orm.xml like this one&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;named-query name=&quot;Test.findAll&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;query&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
       select o&lt;br/&gt;
         from Test o&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/query&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/named-query&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fail to execute with exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error message: org.apache.openjpa.kernel.jpql.TokenMgrError: Lexical error at line 1, column 10.  Encountered: &quot;\n&quot; (10), after : &quot;&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please, add the possibility to the parser to handle multiline queries.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Windows XP</environment>
